The Prelude Replay Code is based on Thomas Wenzel's code who put the Source
of PreludeAMP for ppc.library onto Aminet, and allowed me in an email
to use the Source for my own PPC MPEG Player. Thanks, Thomas.

I myselves mainly adapted the Code to WarpOS/StormC, and i included the
Filerequester/MultiSelect/Program-File features. This Player is Freeware,
but if it does damage to your Sound-Equipment/Computer/Ears/Whatever, i
am not responsible for it (Read: "Standard-Disclaimer").

If you enhance the player in some ways (adding a nicer GUI, adding AHI
Support,...) it would be nice to send me a copy of the modified source,
but this is not required.

